query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, 
       (SELECT pi.url FROM product_images pi WHERE pi.productId = p.id AND pi.isPrimary = 1 LIMIT 1) as primaryImage,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM product_images pi2 WHERE pi2.productId = p.id) as imageCount
FROM products p
ORDER BY p.id;
